      <title>土耳其中央银行会见贷方讨论市场动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkish-central-bank-to-meet-lenders-to-discuss-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据对此事直接了解此事，土耳其中央银行官员将在周日与商业贷方高管会面，这是由于逮捕主要反对派政治家而引发的市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkish-central-bank-to-meet-lenders-to-discuss-market-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 09:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国希望很快达成乌克兰和平协议，因为普京似乎并不着急</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/us-hopes-for-ukraine-peace-deal-soon-as-putin-seems-in-no-hurry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国仍然希望在俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争中发生广泛的停火，即使交战的一面继续在接下来的几天进行谈判之前继续攻击和迹象，克里姆林宫并不急于达成交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/us-hopes-for-ukraine-peace-deal-soon-as-putin-seems-in-no-hurry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 07:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其监狱埃尔多安（Erdogan）的顶级敌人imamoglu，冒着更多动荡的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkey-jails-erdogan-s-top-foe-imamoglu-risking-more-unrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其法院周日正式逮捕了总统雷切普·塔伊普·埃尔多安（Recep Tayyip Erdogan）的最高政治竞争对手，这可能会引发进一步的抗议活动，并在紧张局势时将当地市场保持压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/turkey-jails-erdogan-s-top-foe-imamoglu-risking-more-unrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 07:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-23/israeli-strike-kills-senior-hamas-political-leader-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Deir Al-Balah，加沙地带（AP）＆Mdash;以色列在南加沙地带上罢工至少一夜之间杀死了19名巴勒斯坦人，其中包括哈马斯政治领导人和几名妇女和儿童。居民说，当军方下令撤离时，坦克已进入南部城市拉法的一个地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-03-23/israeli-strike-kills-senior-hamas-political-leader-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 05:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国福利削减了汽车制造商的电动汽车野心的意外风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将英国福利支出减少数十亿英镑的计划可能会产生意外的后果：破坏该国推动零排放车辆销售的推动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/uk-welfare-cuts-pose-unexpected-risk-to-carmakers-ev-ambitions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，在“控制”中遏制乌克兰战争的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/trump-says-efforts-to-contain-war-in-ukraine-under-control</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，阻止俄罗斯和乌克兰之间的战争进一步升级的努力是“控制的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/trump-says-efforts-to-contain-war-in-ukraine-under-control</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 04:25:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国说，随着美国关税织机的震惊，这已经为震惊做好了准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-says-it-s-prepared-for-greater-shocks-as-us-tariffs-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国总理李·昆格（Li Qiang）表示，该国为美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）宣布下个月对其贸易伙伴宣布更多关税的世界准备“超出预期的冲击”做好了准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/china-says-it-s-prepared-for-greater-shocks-as-us-tariffs-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 02:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国宣布紧急状态为第三天的野火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-korea-declares-emergency-as-wildfires-rage-for-third-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国宣布多次森林大火袭击了该国南部，杀死了至少四人，并将数百名居民从家中造成了灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-23/south-korea-declares-emergency-as-wildfires-rage-for-third-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Mar 2025 00:57:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
